summary: This is a Conversion of madutka's "Sucker Punch & Sweetpea Custom Armor" for the Demon Fet Body
descriptionHtml:
[img]https://i.imgur.com/u3popun.png[/img]
This is a SeveNBase Based Conversion of [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/76346/?]madutka's "Sucker Punch & Sweetpea Custom Armor"[/url] for the Demon Fet Body
The Demon Fet Body is a skinner more well endowed version of the [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36992/?]SeveNBase[/url] BombShell.

it is TBBP HDT compatible, with Working weight Slider. Make sure you install the proper requirements listed below


[img]https://i.imgur.com/oQhwEBV.png[/img]
[color=#ff7700]
[/color][b][i][color=#ff7700][size=4][url=http://www.mediafire.com/download/kt4n8a51o8036be/Demon+Fet+Body+%26+-LABIA-.7z][color=#ff7700]Demon Fet Body[/color][/url][/size][/color][/i][/b]   by [url=http://]DeMoNhUnTeR1986
[/url]The Body isn't necessarily required but is here for anyone who might want to try this body out.

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68000/?][b][i][color=#ff7700][size=4]XP32 Maximum Skeleton Extended -XPMSE-[/size][/color][/i][/b][/url]  By [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/3350373/?]Groovtama[/url]

If you for any reason have issues with the xp32 skeletons try downloading [url=http://www.mediafire.com/download/m6h7o7irdj5pm43/Zquad1%27s+Skeleton+for++Demon+Fet+Body.7z#39;s_Skeleton_for__Demon_Fet_Body.7z][color=#ff7700]My Skeleton[/color][/url] & you shouldn't have anymore issues.
[size=4]
[/size][size=4][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36213/?][color=#ff7700]HDT High Heels System[/color][/url][/size][color=#ff7700] [/color] By [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/3701232/?]HydrogensaysHDT[/url]
[img]https://i.imgur.com/hyKTPfg.png[/img]
These are loose files so you will need to install this manually now you can install through NMM but I don't include the FOMOD file.

so just drop the files into your Skyrim directory. the file path for that is  [color=#ffff00]C:/Programs(x86)/Steam/SteamApps/Common/Skyrim/Data[/color].
Now Activate the .ESP by clicking on the "SkyrimLauncher.exe" then Exit out of the Launcher & then click on Loot to finish the activation.
if you need Loot Click here---> [color=#ff7700][url=https://github.com/loot/loot/releases/tag/0.9.1][color=#ff7700]LOOT
[/color][/url][/color]                                                 [img]https://s20.postimg.org/g8llfh1jh/Signature_Final1.jpg[/img]
